metadata.name: AniChest
metadata.description:
We arepreparing to launch a game website where holders can use their cards to fight each others in a tournament,
every single animal with precise fruit skin gonna have his own 3 abilities and they can be upgraded depending on the time the nft is staked,
the first 10 winners will be rewarded some points and they can exchange them in our marketplace to get some of our exclusive items
